        <num>CCRP 2</num>
        <heading>2.  Purpose and construction</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2.  Purpose and construction
The provisions of this Code are intended to provide for the just determination of criminal proceedings.  They shall be construed to secure simplicity in procedure, fairness in administration, and the elimination of unjustifiable delay.</p>
        </content>
